., that we now know would dispossess people around the world through today. Red Round Globe Hot Burning is the culmination of a lifetime of research-encapsulated through an epic tale of love.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aCommonsxHistoryy18th century. 0aPublic landsy18th century. 7aHISTORY / World.2bisacsh  aanthropocene.  acolonialism.  aglobal capitalism.  aglobalism.  aindustrialization.  aprivatization.  aproletariat.  aresistance.  arevolution.  aslavery.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2019 Englishz978311061017808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2019z9783110606195oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUCA Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065207908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066763940uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520971189zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520971189423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520971189.jpg  a978-3-11-061017-8  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-065207-9  UCA Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-066763-9  University of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2019  aZDB-23-DGGb2019